* [[Maurice Fréchet]] (1946) * [[Paul Lévy (mathematician)|Paul Lévy]] (1953) * [[Henri Cartan]] (1959) * [[Szolem Mandelbrojt]] (1965), * [[Jean-Pierre Serre]] (1971) * [[Alexandre Grothendieck]] (1977) * [[André Néron]] (1983) * [[François Bruhat]] (1989) * [[Jean-Pierre Kahane]] (1995) * [[Jacques Dixmier]] (2001) * [[Louis Boutet de Monvel]] (2007) * [[Luc Illusie]] (2012) * [[Yves Colin de Verdière]] (2018) ==References== {{DEFAULTSORT:Emile Picard Medal}} [[Category:French science and technology awards]] [[Category:Mathematics awards]] <references />{{award-stub}}
